      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为这个项目画一个甘特图，时间跨度是2014年1月。首先，日期格式统一用YYYY-MM-DD吧，这样比较清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dateFormat",
        "YYYY-MM-DD"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，日期格式已经设为YYYY-MM-DD。那整体结构怎么划分？需要几个阶段？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "dateFormat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "分两个主要阶段。第一个叫\"Section\"，里面有两个任务：任务A从1月1号开始，持续30天，标记为a1；另一个任务要等A完成后才开始，持续20天。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section",
        "A task",
        "a1",
        "2014-01-01",
        "30d",
        "Another task",
        "after a1",
        "20d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，第一个Section已经加上。A任务从2014-01-01开始30天，标记a1；第二个任务依赖a1，持续20天。那第二个阶段呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section",
        "A task",
        "Another task",
        "a1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第二个阶段叫\"Another\"。里面第一个任务从1月12号开始，持续12天；还有一个任务，持续24天，这个不用指定开始日期，让它紧接前一个任务就行。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section",
        "Another",
        "Task in sec",
        "2014-01-12",
        "12d",
        "another task",
        "24d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：第二个阶段里，\"another task\"的24天也是接在\"Task in sec\"之后对吧？不需要额外标记？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Task in sec",
        "another task",
        "24d"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，就是这个意思。另外整个图加个标题叫\"A Gantt Diagram\"。",
